  <description>
    <p>Do you sit at a computer all day? Posture Parrot is here to help! Posture Parrot is a desktop app that reminds you to have good posture and take breaks throughout the day. It's like having a personal trainer for your ergonomic health!</p>
    <p>Here are some of the features that make Posture Parrot great:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Break reminders: Set reminders to take breaks and stretch throughout the day.</li>
      <li>Customizable reminders: Customize the frequency and timing of your reminders to fit your schedule.</li>
      <!-- <li>Eye exercises: Get reminders to do eye exercises to reduce eye strain from staring at a screen all day.</li> -->
      <li>Cross-platform: Available on Linux and Windows, so you can improve your posture no matter what operating system you use.</li>
      <li>Open source: Posture Parrot is open source, so you can contribute to its development and help make it even better!</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Posture Parrot is ready to help you improve your posture and stay healthy. Download it today and start feeling better!</p>
  </description>
